1. User APIs
Handles authentication and basic user info.

API Purpose                 	HTTP Method	Endpoint
Register / SignUp          	POST	        /user/signup
Get User by ID	                GET	        /user/{id}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. HR APIs
Manages HR profiles and CRUD operations.

API Purpose	        HTTP Method	Endpoint
Register HR            	POST       	/hr/register
Get HR by ID	        GET       	/hr/{id}
Update HR by ID 	PUT        	/hr/{id}
Delete HR by ID	       DELETE          	/hr/{id}
Get All HRs	       GET	         /hr
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Job Seeker APIs
Manages seeker profiles and CRUD operations.

API Purpose	              HTTP Method	Endpoint
Register Job Seeker	      POST         	/jobseeker/register
Get Job Seeker by ID	       GET	       /jobseeker/{id}
Update Job Seeker by ID	       PUT	       /jobseeker/{id}
Delete Job Seeker by ID	       DELETE	       /jobseeker/{id}
Get All Job Seekers	       GET	       /jobseeker
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
ðŸ“Œ Required API Endpoints for Job Posting
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Operation              | Method   | Endpoint                                                  | Purpose                                |
| ---------------------- | -------- | --------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------- |
| Create a job posting   | `POST`   | `/job-posting`                                            | HR posts a new job                     |
| Get all job postings   | `GET`    | `/job-posting`                                            | Retrieve all jobs (open listings)      |
| Get job by ID          | `GET`    | `/job-posting/{id}`                                       | View a specific job                    |
| Update job by ID       | `PUT`    | `/job-posting/{id}`                                       | HR updates job details                 |
| Delete job by ID       | `DELETE` | `/job-posting/{id}`                                       | HR deletes a job listing               |
| Get jobs by HR ID      | `GET`    | `/job-posting/hr/{hrId}`                                  | View all jobs posted by a specific HR  |
| Search jobs (optional) | `GET`    | `/job-posting/search?skills=...&location=...&company=...` | Filter by job title, location, company |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ðŸ“Œ Required API Endpoints for Application
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Operation                          | Method   | Endpoint                                | Role       | Purpose                                               |
| ---------------------------------- | -------- | --------------------------------------- | ---------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| Apply to a job                     | `POST`   | `/applications`                         | Job Seeker | Submit a job application                              |
| View all applications (self)       | `GET`    | `/applications/jobseeker/{jobSeekerId}` | Job Seeker | View all applications submitted by a job seeker       |
| Track application status           | `GET`    | `/applications/status/{applicationId}`  | Job Seeker | Track the status of a specific application            |
| Update application details         | `PUT`    | `/applications/{applicationId}`         | Job Seeker | Update application (e.g., resume, cover letter)       |
| Delete application                 | `DELETE` | `/applications/{applicationId}`         | Job Seeker | Withdraw the application                              |
| View all applications (global)     | `GET`    | `/applications`                         | HR/Admin   | View all submitted applications (for admin/testing)   |
| View applications by filters       | `GET`    | `/applications/filter?...`              | HR         | Search/filter applications by job, status, date, etc. |
| View application by ID             | `GET`    | `/applications/{applicationId}`         | HR         | View a specific application                           |
| View applications by Job ID        | `GET`    | `/applications/job/{jobId}`             | HR         | View applications for a specific job                  |
| View applications by Job Seeker ID | `GET`    | `/applications/jobseeker/{jobSeekerId}` | HR         | View applications from a particular job seeker        |
| Shortlist or Reject application    | `PATCH`  | `/applications/{applicationId}/status`  | HR         | Update application status to shortlisted/rejected     |
| Update interview outcome           | `PATCH`  | `/applications/{applicationId}/outcome` | HR         | Record interview result for an application            |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


ðŸ“Œ Required API Endpoints for Interview
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Operation                                 | Method   | Endpoint                          | Purpose                          |
| ----------------------------------------- | -------- | --------------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Schedule interview                        | `POST`   | `/interviews`                     | HR schedules an interview        |
| Get interview by ID                       | `GET`    | `/interviews/{id}`                | View specific interview details  |
| Get interview by Application              | `GET`    | `/interviews/application/{appId}` | View interview by application    |
| Update interview (status, time, feedback) | `PUT`    | `/interviews/{id}`                | Update interview outcome or time |
| Delete interview (optional)               | `DELETE` | `/interviews/{id}`                | Cancel interview                 |
| Get all interviews (optional)             | `GET`    | `/interviews`                     | Admin or analytics               |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ðŸ“Œ Required API Endpoints for Resume History
| Operation                   | Method   | Endpoint                         | Purpose                            |
| --------------------------- | -------- | -------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Upload new resume           | `POST`   | `/resume-history`                | Add new resume entry               |
| Get resume history for user | `GET`    | `/resume-history/jobseeker/{id}` | List resume versions by job seeker |
| Delete resume (optional)    | `DELETE` | `/resume-history/{id}`           | Delete a resume                    |
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
